headline: Merck opens vaccine manufacturing facility in North Carolina
summary: Merck said on Tuesday it has opened a $1-billion facility at its North Carolina site, as the drugmaker seeks to boost its U.S. manufacturing in the face of President Donald Trump's tariff threats. ...
